genresAdvancedInfo.name: ugandan gospel
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Ugandan gospel music is a vibrant and uplifting genre that draws on traditional African rhythms and harmonies. The genre features powerful vocals and lyrics that celebrate faith, hope, and love. Ugandan gospel artists often use music as a means of spreading positive messages and inspiring listeners to live a more meaningful life.
